Hello on that sunny Tuesday.💞Just what breakfast looked like earlier today.🍽
Can't go wrong with a bowl of coconut oatmeal topped with banana, berries and some coconut chips.🍌😍
✖️My basic oatmeal recipe is already up on my blog. Just add in some coconut flakes and cook it with coconut milk.💁🏼
As usual, I'm off for a run now.✌️Hope your day started well, too.💋Enjoy it!
